	<string id="ui_mcm_menu_EFT_ADS_weapon_handling">
        <text>Weapon Handling Affects Power</text>
    </string>
	<string id="ui_mcm_EFT_ADS_handling_affect">
        <text>Handling Affects Anim Power</text>
    </string>
	<string id="ui_mcm_EFT_ADS_handling_factor">
        <text>Handling Factor On Power</text>
    </string>
	<string id="ui_mcm_EFT_ADS_handling_factor_desc">
        <text>Changes how much handling affects the power, higher means a more pronounced effect. At 4, 100% handling gives 0.2 multiplier, at 1, 100% handling gives 0.5 multiplier. The formula is (factor/(factor + (handling/100)^handling_exponent)) + handling_offset.	</text>
    </string>
	<string id="ui_mcm_EFT_ADS_max_handling_factor">
        <text>Max Handling Multiplier</text>
    </string>
	<string id="ui_mcm_EFT_ADS_handling_exponent">
        <text>Handling Exponent</text>
    </string>
	<string id="ui_mcm_EFT_ADS_handling_exponent_desc">
        <text>Changes the exponent on handling that is used in the formula, for higher values, it means a sharper drop to multiplier. Formula is (factor/(factor + (handling/100)^handling_exponent)) + handling_offset.  </text>
    </string>
	<string id="ui_mcm_EFT_ADS_handling_offset">
        <text>Handling Offset</text>
    </string>
	
